><parsexml> </parsexml></settings></server_item_hatitem></number24><number62><server_questtext_EN><diff><warri002><questtextxml><oldversion> Mission1=Hunting Little Dodo
desc=Hmm, I am actually looking for a new man but not that urgent to hire anyone.

Since it is for Roxbury, I want a proof to know if you are a reliable person to depend on.

Outside this city, there is a large field name Weedridge. See the door on my right? That door is the way that will lead you to Weedridge.

In Weedridge, the monster Dodo's number has risen rapidly. It is not just about the rise of numbers but they are disturbing our farm, attacking farmers and more. If you catch the Little Dodos, I will trust you... how about it? If you finish it I will pay you the right price for it.
runDlg=I will see how you keep your promise.
finishDlg=Ho&#x2026;Already finished?  I like the way you speedly take care of your work. Claris has sent me a nice guy! Here is the right price for your job. I will tell the village people about it. Good work!
</oldversion><newversion> Mission1=Hunting Dodo
desc=Hmm, I am actually looking for a new man but not that urgent to hire anyone.

